<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-08-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-08-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="42" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d42">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName>
                                to Prime Minister <persName type="to">Churchill</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d42fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché,
                                London, via Navy channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-31">31 August 1944</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Number 612, personal and top secret, from the President for the Prime
                            Minister.</p>
                        <p>Your 773.<note n="2" xml:id="d42fn2"><hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>.</note>
                            I am distressed at the news of your illness. Please guard your health
                            first and above all other considerations.</p>
                        <p>We can postpone <gloss target="#t_Octagon1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Octagon</hi></gloss> to some later date if it appears advisable
                            to do so.</p>
                        <p>Where is landing spot? If New York you and I could go to <gloss target="#t_Octagon1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Octagon</hi></gloss>
                            together on my train.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>